    "Turnitin -is not free to use, it is an institutional subscription-based service for similarity checking.",
    "Turnitin differs from most algorithmic AI detection tools in that it also has an extensive proprietary archive of work submitted to Turnitin, in addition to web harvested content, which it can use to check similarity, and to undertake AI checks.",
    "Both assignments were checked by Turnitin.",
    "The original (2018) assignment was correctly found to have 0% AI, whereas on the GPT-4 generated version, Turnitin found that \"32%",
    "of qualifying text in this submission has been determined to be generated by AI.\""
